import { Container, Button, Row, Form, Col } from "react-bootstrap";

const EmployeeCardConstructor = ({
  btnValue,
  editMode,
  firstname,
  department,
  designation,
  mobile,
  email,
  date,
  newFirstnameUpdated,
  newDepartmentUpdated,
  newDesignationUpdated,
  newMobileUpdated,
  newEmailUpdated,
}) => {};


const EmployeeCard = new EmployeeCardConstructor ({
  btnValue,
  editMode,
  firstname,
  department,
  designation,
  mobile,
  email,
  date,
  newFirstnameUpdated,
  newDepartmentUpdated,
  newDesignationUpdated,
  newMobileUpdated,
  newEmailUpdated,
}) 

export default EmployeeCard;
